# CountDown App Features

## Core Features
- Event management with countdown display
- Color customization for events
- Notification system
- Free version with 3 event limit

## Key Components

### Event Management
- [Event.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/Models/Event.swift) defines the event model
- [EventRow.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventRow.swift) displays events in the list
- [EventDetailView.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventDetailView.swift) shows event details

### Countdown Display
- [CountdownDisplay.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/CountdownDisplay.swift) handles countdown visualization
- Supports different display formats (days, hours, minutes)
- Shows special states (today, past events)

### Color System
- [EventColor.swift](mdc:countDown/countDown/Countdown/Countdown/EventColor.swift) defines available colors
- Supports 7 colors: red, orange, yellow, green, blue, purple, pink
- Color selection in event creation/editing

### Notification System
- Event-based notifications
- Configurable notification timing
- Notification settings management

### Data Management
- Firebase integration for data storage
- Local data persistence
- Event synchronization

### UI Components
- List view for events
- Detail view for event information
- Add/Edit event form
- Settings view
- Color picker
- Notification settings
